<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Support</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("header", { headerTitle: "Support" }) %>

  <div class="page-banner">
    <h1>We're Here to Support You</h1>
    <p>You're not alone — help is always available</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="resource-grid">

      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">🚶</div>
        <h3>Take a Break</h3>
        <p>Step outside for a short walk or find a quiet space to breathe and reset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">📞</div>
        <h3>Talk to Someone</h3>
        <p>Reach out to a friend, family member, or someone you trust about how you're feeling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">🧘</div>
        <h3>Mindfulness</h3>
        <p>Try a calming breathing or meditation exercise to stay present and grounded.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">💙</div>
        <h3>Professional Help</h3>
        <p>If you feel persistently low, consider talking to a counsellor or mental health professional.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="card mt-3 text-center" style="background:var(--color-accent);border-color:var(--wsu-red);">
      <h3 style="color:var(--wsu-red);">Need immediate help?</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Call <strong>Lifeline: 13 11 14</strong> (24/7) or <strong>Beyond Blue: 1300 22 4636</strong></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);">In an emergency, call 000</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-3 text-center">
      <a href="/mood" class="btn btn-primary">Log Your Mood</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("footer") %>
</body>

</html>
